@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pljtnp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos(0.70)
    tmp = (v2 / 0.73)
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp((v2 + 0.71 / v2 + 0.78)))
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.77 / tmp + 0.94)) / tmp)
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.22)) * tmp)
    v2 = ((0.27 + wp.cos(tmp + 0.12)) + ((v2 + 0.06 / v1 + 0.41) - (tmp + 0.33 * v1 + 0.70)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v2 + 0.94 * v0 + 0.03)))
    data[tid] = v0
